consts = pyte.create_consts(3)
varnames = pyte.create_varnames('x')
instructions = [pyte.ops.LOAD_CONST(consts[0]), pyte.ops.STORE_FAST(
    varnames[0]), consts[0] + varnames[0], pyte.tokens.RETURN_VALUE]
func = pyte.compile(instructions, consts, varnames=varnames, names=[])
assert func() == 6
